{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886541213,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b161c7d001VG80BGjjYQrzju","messageID":"msg_d7b160ae4001zvxIdvW2D8DRBr","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-d7a00c33e6c1409dbc48691b7041da23","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Specification\n2: \n3: ## Module: manifests\n4: \n5: ### ServiceAccount\n6: \n7: #### ServiceAccount Definition\n8: \n9: ```yaml\n10: apiVersion: v1\n11: kind: ServiceAccount\n12: metadata:\n13:   name: <service-account-name>\n14:   namespace: <namespace>\n15: ```\n16: \n17: **Parameters:**\n18: - `name`: ServiceAccount name\n19: - `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n20: \n21: ### Role\n22: \n23: #### Role Definition\n24: \n25: ```yaml\n26: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n27: kind: Role\n28: metadata:\n29:   name: <role-name>\n30:   namespace: <namespace>\n31: rules:\n32:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n33:     resources: [\"pods\", \"services\", \"configmaps\"]\n34:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n35: ```\n36: \n37: **Parameters:**\n38: - `name`: Role name\n39: - `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n40: - `rules`: List of policy rules\n41: \n42: ### RoleBinding\n43: \n44: #### RoleBinding Definition\n45: \n46: ```yaml\n47: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n48: kind: RoleBinding\n49: metadata:\n50:   name: <role-binding-name>\n51:   namespace: <namespace>\n52: subjects:\n53:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n54:     name: <service-account-name>\n55:     namespace: <namespace>\n56: roleRef:\n57:   kind: Role\n58:   name: <role-name>\n59:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n60: ```\n61: \n62: **Parameters:**\n63: - `name`: RoleBinding name\n64: - `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n65: - `subjects`: List of subjects (ServiceAccounts, Users, Groups)\n66: - `roleRef`: Reference to the Role\n67: \n68: ### ClusterRole (Optional)\n69: \n70: #### ClusterRole Definition\n71: \n72: ```yaml\n73: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n74: kind: ClusterRole\n75: metadata:\n76:   name: <cluster-role-name>\n77: rules:\n78:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n79:     resources: [\"nodes\", \"namespaces\"]\n80:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n81: ```\n82: \n83: **Parameters:**\n84: - `name`: ClusterRole name\n85: - `rules`: List of policy rules\n86: \n87: ### ClusterRoleBinding (Optional)\n88: \n89: #### ClusterRoleBinding Definition\n90: \n91: ```yaml\n92: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n93: kind: ClusterRoleBinding\n94: metadata:\n95:   name: <cluster-role-binding-name>\n96: subjects:\n97:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n98:     name: <service-account-name>\n99:     namespace: <namespace>\n100: roleRef:\n101:   kind: ClusterRole\n102:   name: <cluster-role-name>\n103:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n104: ```\n105: \n106: **Parameters:**\n107: - `name`: ClusterRoleBinding name\n108: - `subjects`: List of subjects\n109: - `roleRef`: Reference to the ClusterRole\n110: \n111: ## Common API Resources\n112: \n113: ### Core API (apiGroups: [\"\"])\n114: \n115: Common resources:\n116: - `pods`\n117: - `services`\n118: - `configmaps`\n119: - `secrets`\n120: - `persistentvolumeclaims`\n121: - `events`\n122: \n123: ### Apps API (apiGroups: [\"apps\"])\n124: \n125: Common resources:\n126: - `deployments`\n127: - `statefulsets`\n128: - `daemonsets`\n129: - `replicasets`\n130: \n131: ## Common Verbs\n132: \n133: - `get`, `list`, `watch` - Read operations\n134: - `create` - Create resources\n135: - `update`, `patch` - Update resources\n136: - `delete` - Delete resources\n137: - `*` - All operations\n138: \n139: ## Best Practices\n140: \n141: - Principle of least privilege\n142: - Namespace-scoped permissions where possible\n143: - Use specific resource names with `resourceNames` field for fine-grained control\n144: - Regular review of RBAC policies\n\n(End of file - total 144 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Specification\n\n## Module: manifests\n\n### ServiceAccount\n\n#### ServiceAccount Definition\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: <service-account-name>\n  namespace: <namespace>\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `name`: ServiceAccount name\n- `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md","time":{"start":1775886541194,"end":1775886541212}}}}
