{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886568239,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b1677d6001xDoRqOvq6y8c5n","messageID":"msg_d7b165917001LOqXto4FYggGxq","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-887720a3997d4e8dbb0c36dd9db1dfb3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-035\n- **Title**: client-go 类型客户端生成\n- **Module**: client-go\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: L\n- **Status**: Not Started\n\n## Description\n\n为 AgentCube 平台的 Kubernetes 自定义资源（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 等）生成基于 client-go 的类型化客户端库，提供强类型的 Kubernetes API 访问能力。\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Kubernetes cluster\n- CRD definitions for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n- Go 1.19+\n\n## Related Changes\n\nNone\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n## Deferred Items\n\n[To be filled during implementation]","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/CHANGE.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/CHANGE.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775886568227,"end":1775886568238}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886568242,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b168b00001tVS6DvyFosDb4Z","messageID":"msg_d7b165917001LOqXto4FYggGxq","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-f6b2c4c145604550a990ae7f5f3291a5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-035 Implementation Notes\n\n## Implementation Status\n- [ ] client-go clientset structure\n- [ ] AgentRuntime client implementation\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter client implementation\n- [ ] Informer implementation for AgentRuntime\n- [ ] Informer implementation for CodeInterpreter\n- [ ] Lister implementation\n- [ ] Client tests\n- [ ] Documentation\n- [ ] Examples\n\n## Implementation Details\n\n### Files Created\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### Test Coverage\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### Client API Design\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/README.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/README.md","time":{"start":1775886568231,"end":1775886568240}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775886568271,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b168b32001Z196GJrewKLboa","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7b165917001LOqXto4FYggGxq","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":42320,"input":87,"output":441,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":41792}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775886569443,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b168fe00014MdypwRWZ4omoh","messageID":"msg_d7b168b660014Q59OryVF1Jvdg","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886680204,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b184034001s76k2lw5TnpBgZ","messageID":"msg_d7b168b660014Q59OryVF1Jvdg","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-8f8d1f7dbc3c49dfab4010166421bc9b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## Overview\n\n为 AgentCube 平台生成基于 Kubernetes client-go 的类型化客户端库，提供对自定义资源（AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter 等）的强类型 API 访问能力，支持 CRUD 操作、Watch 机制和 Informer 模式。\n\n## Purpose\n\nclient-go 类型客户端是 AgentCube 平台开发者工具链的核心组成部分，旨在：\n\n1. **类型安全** - 提供编译时类型检查，避免运行时错误\n2. **开发效率** - 简化 Kubernetes API 调用，提供简洁的开发体验\n3. **标准化接口** - 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 最佳实践和约定\n4. **高性能** - 支持高效的 Watch 和 Informer 机制\n5. **可维护性** - 自动生成客户端代码，与 CRD 定义保持同步\n\n## Module\n\n`client-go` - Go 客户端库\n\n## Language\n\nGo\n\n## Size\n\nL\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **ClientSet 生成**\n   - AgentRuntime client\n   - CodeInterpreter client\n   - 支持所有 Kubernetes API verbs (get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete)\n\n2. **Typed Client**\n   - Namespace-scoped operations\n   - Cluster-scoped operations (如需要)\n   - 支持子资源 (status, scale)\n\n3. **Informer 集成**\n   - AgentRuntime informer\n   - CodeInterpreter informer\n   - 事件处理器支持\n   - 缓存机制\n\n4. **Lister 支持**\n   - AgentRuntime lister\n   - CodeInterpreter lister\n   - 高效的只读访问\n\n5. **代码生成工具**\n   - code-generator 配置\n   - 自定义代码生成脚本\n   - 自动化文档生成\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- 其他语言的客户端（Python、Java 等）\n- 跨平台的客户端生成\n- gRPC 客户端生成\n- REST API 直接调用封装\n- CLI 工具集成\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Components Impacted\n\n1. **Controller Manager**\n   - 需要使用生成的客户端管理 AgentRuntime\n   - 需要 Informer 监听资源变更\n\n2. **Workload Manager**\n   - 需要使用生成的客户端创建和管理 AgentRuntime\n   - 需要访问 AgentRuntime status\n\n3. **外部工具和脚本**\n   - 需要使用客户端进行资源操作\n   - 需要 Watch 机制监听资源事件\n\n### Dependencies\n\n- **Go 1.19+**: 客户端库开发语言\n- **Kubernetes 1.20+**: API 兼容性\n- **k8s.io/code-generator**: 代码生成工具\n- **k8s.io/client-go**: Kubernetes 客户端库基础\n\n### Breaking Changes\n\n无破坏性变更。客户端库是新增的 Go 模块。\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n### 使用 code-generator 生成客户端\n\n**选择**: 使用 Kubernetes 官方的 code-generator 工具\n\n**理由**:\n- 官方维护，稳定可靠\n- 与 Kubernetes API 版本同步\n- 支持所有 Kubernetes API 特性\n- 广泛使用，社区成熟\n\n**示例**:\n```bash\ngo run k8s.io/code-generator/cmd/client-gen \\\n  --input-base=\"github.com/agentcube/apis\" \\\n  --input=\"runtime/v1alpha1\" \\\n  --clientset-path=\"github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client\"\n```\n\n### 包结构组织\n\n**选择**: 遵循 Kubernetes client-go 标准包结构\n\n**理由**:\n- 与 Kubernetes 生态保持一致\n- 便于开发者理解和使用\n- 支持未来扩展\n\n**包结构**:\n```\nclient-go/\n├── pkg/\n│   ├── apis/\n│   │   └── runtime/\n│   │       └── v1alpha1/\n│   │           ├── doc.go\n│   │           ├── register.go\n│   │           ├── types.go\n│   │           ├── agentruntime_types.go\n│   │           └── codeinterpreter_types.go\n│   ├── client/\n│   │   ├── clientset/\n│   │   │   └── versioned/\n│   │   │       ├── clientset.go\n│   │   │       ├── doc.go\n│   │   │       ├── fake/\n│   │   │       └── typed/\n│   │   │           └── runtime/\n│   │   │               └── v1alpha1/\n│   │   │                   ├── agentruntime.go\n│   │   │                   ├── codeinterpreter.go\n│   │   │                   ├── fake/\n│   │   │                   │   ├── agentruntime.go\n│   │   │                   │   └── codeinterpreter.go\n│   │   │                   ├── generated_expansion.go\n│   │   │                   └── runtime_client.go\n│   ├── informers/\n│   │   └── externalversions/\n│   │       ├── internalinterfaces/\n│   │       └── runtime/\n│   │           └── v1alpha1/\n│   │               ├── agentruntime.go\n│   │               ├── codeinterpreter.go\n│   │               └── interface.go\n│   └── listers/\n│       └── runtime/\n│           └── v1alpha1/\n│               ├── agentruntime.go\n│               └── codeinterpreter.go\n├── go.mod\n├── go.sum\n├── Makefile\n└── README.md\n```\n\n### API Group 和 Version 命名\n\n**选择**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n**理由**:\n- 遵循 Kubernetes API group 命名约定\n- `runtime` 表示运行时相关资源\n- `agentcube.volcano.sh` 表示 AgentCube 项目域名\n- `v1alpha1` 表示初始 API 版本\n\n### 自动化代码生成\n\n**选择**: 使用 Makefile 自动化代码生成流程\n\n**理由**:\n- 标准化代码生成流程\n- 易于集成到 CI/CD\n- 确保代码与 CRD 定义同步\n\n**Makefile 示例**:\n```makefile\nCODEGEN_PKG := $(shell go env GOPATH)/pkg/mod/k8s.io/code-generator@$(shell go list -m -f '{{.Version}}' k8s.io/code-generator)\n\ngenerate: codegen\n\t@echo \"Generation complete\"\n\ncodegen:\n\t@echo \"Generating client code...\"\n\tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/client-gen/main.go \\\n\t\t--input-base=github.com/agentcube/apis \\\n\t\t--input=runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n\t\t--clientset-path=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client \\\n\t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\n\n\tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/informer-gen/main.go \\\n\t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n\t\t--versioned-clientset-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/client/clientset/versioned \\\n\t\t--listers-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/listers \\\n\t\t--output-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/informers \\\n\t\t--output-base=.\n\n\tgo run $(CODEGEN_PKG)/cmd/lister-gen/main.go \\\n\t\t--input-dirs=github.com/agentcube/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 \\\n\t\t--output-package=github.com/agentcube/client-go/pkg/listers\n```\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: 手动编写客户端代码\n\n**描述**: 手动编写所有客户端代码\n\n**优点**:\n- 完全控制代码实现\n- 可以自定义优化\n\n**缺点**:\n- 维护成本高\n- 容易出错\n- 难以与 CRD 定义同步\n- 违反 DRY 原则\n\n**选择**: 不采纳 - 使用 code-generator 自动生成\n\n### Alternative 2: 使用其他代码生成工具\n\n**描述**: 使用 kubebuilder 或 operator-framework 的代码生成\n\n**优点**:\n- 与 Controller-Runtime 集成\n- 提供更多高级功能\n\n**缺点**:\n- 引入额外依赖\n- 可能过于重量级\n- 生成的代码可能不符合我们的需求\n\n**选择**: 不采纳 - 使用轻量级的 code-generator\n\n### Alternative 3: 直接使用 REST API\n\n**描述**: 不生成类型化客户端，直接使用 REST API\n\n**优点**:\n- 无需生成代码\n- 语言无关\n\n**缺点**:\n- 缺乏类型安全\n- 开发效率低\n- 容易出错\n- 无法利用编译时检查\n\n**选择**: 不采纳 - 类型安全对 Go 项目至关重要\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: 项目初始化 (Day 1)\n\n1. 创建 client-go 目录结构\n2. 初始化 Go module\n3. 配置 go.mod 依赖\n4. 创建基础目录\n5. 设置 Makefile\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] 目录结构创建\n- [ ] Go module 初始化\n- [ ] 依赖配置\n- [ ] Makefile 创建\n\n### Phase 2: API 类型定义 (Day 1-2)\n\n1. 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录\n2. 定义 doc.go\n3. 定义 register.go\n4. 定义 types.go\n5. 定义 AgentRuntime 类型\n6. 定义 CodeInterpreter 类型\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] doc.go 创建\n- [ ] register.go 创建\n- [ ] types.go 创建\n- [ ] AgentRuntime 类型定义\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n### Phase 3: 代码生成配置 (Day 2)\n\n1. 配置 code-generator 参数\n2. 创建代码生成脚本\n3. 配置 Makefile 目标\n4. 测试代码生成\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] code-generator 配置\n- [ ] 生成脚本创建\n- [ ] Makefile 目标配置\n- [ ] 代码生成测试\n\n### Phase 4: ClientSet 生成 (Day 2-3)\n\n1. 生成 clientset 代码\n2. 验证生成的接口\n3. 测试 CRUD 操作\n4. 测试 namespace-scoped 操作\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] clientset 生成\n- [ ] 接口验证\n- [ ] CRUD 测试\n- [ ] namespace 测试\n\n### Phase 5: Informer 生成 (Day 3-4)\n\n1. 生成 informer 代码\n2. 实现 AgentRuntime informer\n3. 实现 CodeInterpreter informer\n4. 测试事件处理\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] informer 生成\n- [ ] AgentRuntime informer\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter informer\n- [ ] 事件处理测试\n\n### Phase 6: Lister 生成 (Day 4)\n\n1. 生成 lister 代码\n2. 实现 AgentRuntime lister\n3. 实现 CodeInterpreter lister\n4. 测试只读访问\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] lister 生成\n- [ ] AgentRuntime lister\n- [ ] CodeInterpreter lister\n- [ ] 只读访问测试\n\n### Phase 7: 测试和验证 (Day 4-5)\n\n1. 编写单元测试\n2. 编写集成测试\n3. 测试所有 API 操作\n4. 测试错误处理\n5. 性能测试\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] 单元测试\n- [ ] 集成测试\n- [ ] API 测试\n- [ ] 错误处理测试\n- [ ] 性能测试\n\n### Phase 8: 文档和示例 (Day 5)\n\n1. 编写 README.md\n2. 编写 API 文档\n3. 创建使用示例\n4. 编写最佳实践指南\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] README.md\n- [ ] API 文档\n- [ ] 使用示例\n- [ ] 最佳实践指南\n\n### Phase 9: CI/CD 集成 (Day 5-6)\n\n1. 配置 CI pipeline\n2. 自动化代码生成\n3. 自动化测试\n4. 发布流程\n\n**检查清单**:\n- [ ] CI 配置\n- [ ] 自动化生成\n- [ ] 自动化测试\n- [ ] 发布流程\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n1. **Client 测试**\n   - 测试 CRUD 操作\n   - 测试错误处理\n   - 测试参数验证\n\n2. **Informer 测试**\n   - 测试事件触发\n   - 测试缓存更新\n   - 测试处理器注册\n\n3. **Lister 测试**\n   - 测试资源查询\n   - 测试缓存命中\n   - 测试 namespace 过滤\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n1. **ClientSet 集成测试**\n   - 连接真实 Kubernetes 集群\n   - 测试完整 CRUD 流程\n   - 测试并发操作\n\n2. **Informer 集成测试**\n   - 测试实时事件监听\n   - 测试多客户端同步\n   - 测试重连机制\n\n3. **Lister 集成测试**\n   - 测试大规模资源查询\n   - 测试缓存一致性\n   - 测试性能指标\n\n### End-to-End Tests\n\n1. **完整工作流测试**\n   - 创建资源\n   - Watch 资源变更\n   - 更新资源\n   - 删除资源\n\n2. **错误恢复测试**\n   - 测试网络故障\n   - 测试 API 服务器故障\n   - 测试重连机制\n\n3. **性能测试**\n   - 测试高并发场景\n   - 测试大规模资源操作\n   - 测试内存使用\n\n## API Specification\n\n### AgentRuntime Client API\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (result *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n}\n```\n\n### CodeInterpreter Client API\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, codeInterpreter *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (result *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n}\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n### Go Module 配置\n\n```go\nmodule github.com/agentcube/client-go\n\ngo 1.19\n\nrequire (\n    k8s.io/api v0.26.0\n    k8s.io/apimachinery v0.26.0\n    k8s.io/client-go v0.26.0\n    k8s.io/code-generator v0.26.0\n)\n```\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n1. **身份验证**\n   - 支持 kubeconfig 配置\n   - 支持 ServiceAccount token\n   - 支持 TLS 证书\n\n2. **授权**\n   - 遵循 Kubernetes RBAC\n   - 权限检查\n   - 审计日志\n\n3. **数据安全**\n   - 敏感数据加密\n   - 安全的日志记录\n   - 错误信息脱敏\n\n## Performance Considerations\n\n1. **缓存策略**\n   - Informer 本地缓存\n   - 高效的缓存更新\n   - 缓存一致性保证\n\n2. **并发控制**\n   - 连接池管理\n   - 请求限流\n   - 并发安全\n\n3. **资源使用**\n   - 内存优化\n   - Goroutine 管理\n   - 连接复用\n\n## Monitoring and Metrics\n\n### 关键指标\n\n1. **客户端指标**\n   - API 调用延迟\n   - API 调用成功率\n   - API 调用频率\n\n2. **Informer 指标**\n   - 事件处理延迟\n   - 缓存命中率\n   - 同步状态\n\n3. **Lister 指标**\n   - 查询延迟\n   - 缓存大小\n   - 查询频率\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- 成功生成完整的 client-go 客户端库\n- 所有 CRUD 操作正常工作\n- Informer 和 Lister 功能完善\n- 测试覆盖率达到 80% 以上\n- 文档完整清晰\n- 示例代码可用\n- CI/CD 集成完成\n\n## References\n\n- [Kubernetes client-go Documentation](https://github.com/kubernetes/client-go)\n- [Kubernetes code-generator](https://github.com/kubernetes/code-generator)\n- [AgentCube Spec](../../spec.md)\n- [AR-035 Spec](./spec.md)\n- [Kubernetes API Conventions](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775886680196,"end":1775886680201}}}}
