{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775886736268,"sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","part":{"id":"prt_d7b191b73001nrURA5MOEsCyzr","messageID":"msg_d7b1840b2001bhrudgjrPtjN4F","sessionID":"ses_284ea1c7dffeW7xKCHghFbOWeg","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-e2cbd54cb3cf4105b78c871e06be0390","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 Specification\n\n## Module: client-go\n\n### ClientSet\n\n#### ClientSet Definition\n\n```go\ntype Interface interface {\n    Runtime() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n    Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n}\n```\n\n#### RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n\n```go\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n    RESTClient() rest.Interface\n    AgentRuntimes(agentRuntime string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n    CodeInterpreters(codeInterpreter string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n}\n```\n\n### AgentRuntime Client\n\n#### AgentRuntimeInterface\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, listOpts metav1.ListOptions, deleteOpts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n}\n```\n\n#### AgentRuntime Methods\n\n**Create**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.CreateOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n- **Description**: Create a new AgentRuntime resource\n\n**Update**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n- **Description**: Update an existing AgentRuntime resource\n\n**UpdateStatus**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `opts metav1.UpdateOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n- **Description**: Update the status subresource of an AgentRuntime\n\n**Delete**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n- **Returns**: `error`\n- **Description**: Delete an AgentRuntime resource by name\n\n**Get**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n- **Description**: Get an AgentRuntime resource by name\n\n**List**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList`, `error`\n- **Description**: List AgentRuntime resources\n\n**Watch**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n- **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n- **Description**: Watch for AgentRuntime resource changes\n\n**Patch**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime`, `error`\n- **Description**: Patch an AgentRuntime resource\n\n### CodeInterpreter Client\n\n#### CodeInterpreterInterface\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterInterface interface {\n