me string`, `opts metav1.DeleteOptions`\n- **Returns**: `error`\n- **Description**: Delete a CodeInterpreter resource by name\n\n**Get**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `opts metav1.GetOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n- **Description**: Get a CodeInterpreter resource by name\n\n**List**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList`, `error`\n- **Description**: List CodeInterpreter resources\n\n**Watch**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `opts metav1.ListOptions`\n- **Returns**: `watch.Interface`, `error`\n- **Description**: Watch for CodeInterpreter resource changes\n\n**Patch**\n- **Parameters**: `ctx context.Context`, `name string`, `pt types.PatchType`, `data []byte`, `opts metav1.PatchOptions`, `subresources ...string`\n- **Returns**: `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`, `error`\n- **Description**: Patch a CodeInterpreter resource\n\n### Informer\n\n#### AgentRuntimeInformer\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInformer interface {\n    Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n    Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreterInformer\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterInformer interface {\n    Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n    Lister() runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n}\n```\n\n### Lister\n\n#### AgentRuntimeLister\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, err error)\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n    AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreterLister\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) (ret []*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, err error)\n    CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister\n    CodeInterpreterListerExpansion\n}\n```\n\n## Common Types\n\n### API Verbs\n\nCommon verbs for API operations